  Submits a raw transaction (serialized, hex-encoded) to local node and network.
  
  Parameters:
  1. hexstring (string, required) - The hex string of the raw transaction
  2. maxfeerate (numeric, optional, default=0.10) - Reject transactions whose fee rate is higher than the specified value
  
  Returns the transaction hash in hex if successful.
  
  Note: This is a sample transaction hex. Replace with your actual signed transaction data.
  The transaction must be properly signed and valid to be accepted by the network.
